{"tid":1024091,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"古天樂孫紅雷將加入《角頭3》　「角頭宇宙」延伸到Netflix","createTime":"2019-02-16T09:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T11:16:34.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"43f7123e83602be5c019498e0148ac556632c924","tid":1024091,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"《角頭》版圖大拓展，第3部曲的《角頭前傳》已開拍，今電影公司宣布接下來的《角頭3》，除了原有的主角鄭人碩、張再興、黃尚禾和唐振剛、吳震亞之外，香港金像獎影帝古天樂和中國大腕孫紅雷也加入，陣容再提升至跨及兩岸三地。<br />\n<br />\n2015年的《角頭》全台賣了8000萬元台幣，去年的《角頭2：王者再起》上升賣到1.27億，並提名金馬獎最佳男配角及新演員。監製張威縯透露，《角頭3》目前加入香港太陽娛樂的資金，目前已近4億資本，導演和《角頭前傳》一樣是台灣的姜瑞智，預計明年2月開拍。之後還計畫與Netflix恰談《角頭影集》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20190216/1518537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190216%2F1518537&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=689603f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190216%2F1518537&h=271e23b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20190216/1518537</a><br />\n<br />\n古生講普通話？"},{"pid":"4016be1666a9a9f979b0d55cfa7e529341e8a2a3","tid":1024091,"uid":38601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T17:52:42.000Z","msg":"留意返 古天樂第一次拍唔係香港人執導既電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe30cc94507685541d9f9699527aca969a53e944","tid":1024091,"uid":45888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T20:14:15.000Z","msg":"又洗米"},{"pid":"c3ce1ead805598a2930cc7dc0ac4bba2c728efb9","tid":1024091,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T20:15:11.000Z","msg":"神者撚 撚大撚"},{"pid":"8a1e2ee3d7d7d37aad0a90157cab66417643b318","tid":1024091,"uid":31173,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T20:17:41.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢角頭"},{"pid":"58e366f24e2f907c4df4568d2ea20c08346e0229","tid